      "anthropic_claude_with_search_latest": {
        "text": "# Recommended Angel Investor Clubs and Networks\n\nHere are some of the most reputable angel investor groups you should consider contacting for your startup:\n\n## Top-Tier Angel Networks\n\n1. **[Tech Coast Angels](https://www.techcoastangels.com/)** - One of the largest and most active angel networks in the US, focused on Southern California with multiple chapters.\n\n2. **[Band of Angels](https://www.bandangels.com/)** - Silicon Valley-based group of former and current high-tech executives investing in early-stage startups.\n\n3. **[Keiretsu Forum](https://keiretsuforum.com/)** - Global angel investment network with chapters across North America, Europe, and Asia.\n\n4. **[Golden Seeds](https://goldenseeds.com/)** - One of the most active investment firms in the US, focused on women-led businesses.\n\n5. **[Hub Angels](https://hubangels.com/)** - Boston-based angel investment group focused on early-stage tech companies.\n\n## Major Regional Networks\n\n6. **[New York Angels](https://www.newyorkangels.com/)** - One of the most active angel groups on the East Coast.\n\n7. **[Houston Angel Network](https://www.houstonangelnetwork.org/)** - Leading angel group in Texas.\n\n8. **[Alliance of Angels](https://www.allianceofangels.com/)** - Pacific Northwest's largest angel organization based in Seattle.\n\n9. **[Great North Ventures](https://greatnorthvc.com/)** - Focused on Minnesota and the Upper Midwest.\n\n## Specialized Groups\n\n10. **[Cambridge Angels](https://cambridgeangels.com/)** - UK-based network for accredited investors (if you're considering international funding).\n\n11. **[Angel Capital Association](https://www.angelcapitalassociation.org/)** - North American professional alliance of angel groups - great resource to find local groups through their directory.\n\n## Online Platforms\n\n12. **[AngelList](https://www.angellist.com/)** - Major online platform connecting startups with angel investors.\n\n13. **[Gust](https://gust.com/)** - Platform that connects startups with angel groups globally.\n\n14. **[SeedInvest](https://www.seedinvest.com/)** - Equity crowdfunding platform that includes angel investors.\n\n## Tips for Approaching Angel Groups:\n\n- Research each group's investment thesis and portfolio to ensure alignment\n- Most angel groups have application processes on their websites\n- Prepare a strong pitch deck and executive summary\n- Be ready to explain your traction, market size, and competitive advantage\n- Consider your startup's stage, industry, and location when selecting groups\n\n**Which industry is your startup in and where are you located?** This would help me provide more targeted recommendations from this list or suggest additional specialized groups.",
        "html": "<h1>Recommended Angel Investor Clubs and Networks</h1>\n<p>Here are some of the most reputable angel investor groups you should consider contacting for your startup:</p>\n<h2>Top-Tier Angel Networks</h2>\n<ol>\n<li><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.techcoastangels.com/\">Tech Coast Angels</a></strong> - One of the largest and most active angel networks in the US, focused on Southern California with multiple chapters.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.bandangels.com/\">Band of Angels</a></strong> - Silicon Valley-based group of former and current high-tech executives investing in early-stage startups.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong><a href=\"https://keiretsuforum.com/\">Keiretsu Forum</a></strong> - Global angel investment network with chapters across North America, Europe, and Asia.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong><a href=\"https://goldenseeds.com/\">Golden Seeds</a></strong> - One of the most active investment firms in the US, focused on women-led businesses.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong><a href=\"https://hubangels.com/\">Hub Angels</a></strong> - Boston-based angel investment group focused on early-stage tech companies.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Major Regional Networks</h2>\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.newyorkangels.com/\">New York Angels</a></strong> - One of the most active angel groups on the East Coast.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.houstonangelnetwork.org/\">Houston Angel Network</a></strong> - Leading angel group in Texas.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.allianceofangels.com/\">Alliance of Angels</a></strong> - Pacific Northwest&#39;s largest angel organization based in Seattle.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong><a href=\"https://greatnorthvc.com/\">Great North Ventures</a></strong> - Focused on Minnesota and the Upper Midwest.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Specialized Groups</h2>\n<ol start=\"10\">\n<li><p><strong><a href=\"https://cambridgeangels.com/\">Cambridge Angels</a></strong> - UK-based network for accredited investors (if you&#39;re considering international funding).</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.angelcapitalassociation.org/\">Angel Capital Association</a></strong> - North American professional alliance of angel groups - great resource to find local groups through their directory.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Online Platforms</h2>\n<ol start=\"12\">\n<li><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.angellist.com/\">AngelList</a></strong> - Major online platform connecting startups with angel investors.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong><a href=\"https://gust.com/\">Gust</a></strong> - Platform that connects startups with angel groups globally.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.seedinvest.com/\">SeedInvest</a></strong> - Equity crowdfunding platform that includes angel investors.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Tips for Approaching Angel Groups:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Research each group&#39;s investment thesis and portfolio to ensure alignment</li>\n<li>Most angel groups have application processes on their websites</li>\n<li>Prepare a strong pitch deck and executive summary</li>\n<li>Be ready to explain your traction, market size, and competitive advantage</li>\n<li>Consider your startup&#39;s stage, industry, and location when selecting groups</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Which industry is your startup in and where are you located?</strong> This would help me provide more targeted recommendations from this list or suggest additional specialized groups.</p>\n"
      },
