        "text": "For your startup, I recommend contacting established **angel investor groups and platforms** known for their strong networks, industry focus, and founder-friendly approaches:\n\n| Angel Investor Club          | Key Features & Focus Areas                                    | Best For                      | Location               | Website Link                                  |\n|-----------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------|-------------------------------|------------------------|----------------------------------------------|\n| **Tech Coast Angels (TCA)** | Over 400 accredited investors; mentorship plus capital; strong in medtech, SaaS, IoT, fintech | Seed and early-stage tech startups | Southern California | [Tech Coast Angels info](https://orielipo.com/top-13-angel-investor-groups-to-fuel-your-startups-growth/) [[2]](https://finmark.com/how-to-find-angel-investors/)[[1]](https://orielipo.com/top-13-angel-investor-groups-to-fuel-your-startups-growth/) |\n| **Golden Seeds**             | Focus on women-founded/led startups; consumer products, tech, software | Women-led startups             | US-wide               | [Golden Seeds info](https://orielipo.com/top-13-angel-investor-groups-to-fuel-your-startups-growth/) [[1]](https://orielipo.com/top-13-angel-investor-groups-to-fuel-your-startups-growth/) |\n| **Pasadena Angels**          | Up to $1.5M early-stage funding; emphasis on scalable startups | California-based early-stage startups | California            | [Pasadena Angels info](https://orielipo.com/top-13-angel-investor-groups-to-fuel-your-startups-growth/) [[1]](https://orielipo.com/top-13-angel-investor-groups-to-fuel-your-startups-growth/)[[4]](https://startupsavant.com/best-angel-investor-groups) |\n| **Alliance of Angels**       | Seattle-based; invests $10M+ annually; strong in IT startups and mentorship | Early-stage, Northwest startups | Seattle               | [Alliance of Angels info](https://orielipo.com/top-13-angel-investor-groups-to-fuel-your-startups-growth/) [[1]](https://orielipo.com/top-13-angel-investor-groups-to-fuel-your-startups-growth/)[[4]](https://startupsavant.com/best-angel-investor-groups) |\n| **Band of Angels**           | Silicon Valley’s first high-tech angel group; over 165 angels | Tech and life sciences startups | Menlo Park, California | [Band of Angels info](https://startupsavant.com/best-angel-investor-groups) [[4]](https://startupsavant.com/best-angel-investor-groups) |\n| **New York Angels**          | Focus on fintech, blockchain, life sciences; strong early-stage background | Northeast-based tech startups  | New York              | [New York Angels info](https://startupsavant.com/best-angel-investor-groups) [[4]](https://startupsavant.com/best-angel-investor-groups) |\n| **Angel Investment Network** | Global platform with 285,000+ angels; searchable by industry & location; supportive resources | Startups at all stages, any industry | Worldwide             | [Angel Investment Network](https://angelinvestmentnetwork.us) [[2]](https://finmark.com/how-to-find-angel-investors/)[[3]](https://startupsavant.com/startup-center/best-angel-investor-websites)[[14]](https://www.angelinvestmentnetwork.us) |\n| **AngelList**                | Founder-friendly platform to connect directly with angels; widely used for early funding | Early-stage startups          | Worldwide             | [AngelList](https://angel.co) [[3]](https://startupsavant.com/startup-center/best-angel-investor-websites) |\n| **Angel Capital Association (ACA)** | Non-profit trade association with 15,000+ high-quality members; educational resources and advocacy | Startups seeking credible vetted investors | Primarily USA, global members | [ACA](https://angelcapitalassociation.org) [[3]](https://startupsavant.com/startup-center/best-angel-investor-websites)[[8]](https://angelcapitalassociation.org/entrepreneurs/)[[13]](https://angelcapitalassociation.org) |\n\nAdditional specialized groups include **Life Science Angels** for healthcare/life sciences startups and regional clubs if you are based in Europe or Switzerland, like Business Angels Switzerland or Geneva Angel Investor Network[[15]](https://seedblink.com/blog/top-angel-clubs-and-investment-networks-in-switzerland).\n\nPlatforms like **Republic** and **StartEngine** also cater to crowdfunding but are more equity crowd-focused rather than exclusive angel clubs.\n\nIf you specify your startup’s industry, stage, or location, I could help narrow the best angel groups further. The above list highlights reputable, established options with a track record to fuel startup growth in 2025. \n\nLinks provided direct you to official or comprehensive sources to connect and learn more from each group or platform.\n\n# CITATIONS\n\n1. [orielipo.com/top-13-angel-investor-groups-to-fuel-your-startups-growth/](https://orielipo.com/top-13-angel-investor-groups-to-fuel-your-startups-growth/)\n\n2. [finmark.com/how-to-find-angel-investors/](https://finmark.com/how-to-find-angel-investors/)\n\n3. [startupsavant.com/startup-center/best-angel-investor-websites](https://startupsavant.com/startup-center/best-angel-investor-websites)\n\n4. [startupsavant.com/best-angel-investor-groups](https://startupsavant.com/best-angel-investor-groups)\n\n5. [www.betaboom.com/magazine/article/top-angel-investors](https://www.betaboom.com/magazine/article/top-angel-investors)\n\n6. [www.angelinvestmentnetwork.us/angel-investor-groups](https://www.angelinvestmentnetwork.us/angel-investor-groups)\n\n7. [eqvista.com/top-100-active-angel-investors-list-for-startups/](https://eqvista.com/top-100-active-angel-investors-list-for-startups/)\n\n8. [angelcapitalassociation.org/entrepreneurs/](https://angelcapitalassociation.org/entrepreneurs/)\n\n9. [waveup.com/blog/top-angel-investing-platforms/](https://waveup.com/blog/top-angel-investing-platforms/)\n\n10. [fundersclub.com/learn/startup-investing/angel-investing/angel-groups/](https://fundersclub.com/learn/startup-investing/angel-investing/angel-groups/)\n\n11. [www.startupfrequency.com/investors/](https://www.startupfrequency.com/investors/?type=Angel+Group)\n\n12. [visible.vc/blog/how-to-find-angel-investors-for-your-startup/](https://visible.vc/blog/how-to-find-angel-investors-for-your-startup/)\n\n13. [angelcapitalassociation.org/](https://angelcapitalassociation.org)\n\n14. [www.angelinvestmentnetwork.us/](https://www.angelinvestmentnetwork.us)\n\n15. [seedblink.com/blog/top-angel-clubs-and-investment-networks-in-switzerland](https://seedblink.com/blog/top-angel-clubs-and-investment-networks-in-switzerland)\n",
